########################################
# CLUB MANAGEMENT
########################################

### List All Clubs  -----WORKS---
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Club   -----WORKS---
POST {{baseUrl}}create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "New Club",
  "about": "A community for technology lovers to share ideas and collaborate"
}

### Get Club Details ---WORKS---
GET {{baseUrl}}{{clubId}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### List All Members---WORKS---
GET {{baseUrl}}{{clubId}}/members/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### Join Club---WORKS---
POST {{baseUrl}}{{clubId}}/join/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}



### Update Club (Admin Only) ___WORKS---
PATCH {{baseUrl}}{{clubId}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "about": "Updated description for the club",
  "avatar": "https://example.com/new-avatar.jpg"
}



### Delete Club (Admin Only) ---WORKS---
DELETE {{baseUrl}}{{clubId}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}



### Leave Club---WORKS---
POST {{baseUrl}}{{clubId}}/leave/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}









